---
title: Hearty Pork & Oregano Pie with Cheesy Mash Top & Balsamic Radish Salad
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm and comforting with this rich, cheesy
mash-topped number. It's just like Nonna used to make (but better!).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64f9d0682eb286838b395039-4cf943f5.jpeg
